{"tid":595241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［討論］食桃同奇異果應唔應該連皮食","createTime":"2018-03-16T12:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T16:08:12.000Z","uid":30213,"like":10,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"640084cb6bf3136873fd8b700ab0a184500c1282","tid":595241,"uid":30213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:58:15.000Z","msg":"今日同個朋友傾傾下計傾到食奇異果<br />\n朋友:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :吓！我由細到大食奇異果都係連皮食咖喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你痴線咖  咁多毛點食<br />\n<br />\n然後佢笑到痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢直頭當我假膠講個笑話佢聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我就再問個大路啲嘅例子<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁你食桃會唔會連皮就咁咬？桃夠都係毛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：吓點會  不嬲食桃都係批咗個皮先食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後佢又笑到痴咗線...<br />\n<br />\n咁算啦 我諗係我同佢唔同姐 跟住就再問多幾個朋友<br />\n<br />\n點知全撚部都話唔會食皮...<br />\n<br />\n到底大家食桃同奇異果會唔會連皮食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會 啲皮咁有益養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會 咁撚多毛點食係咪痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a49f3e1437db0e01afd83be114fc6d67e9a919b","tid":595241,"uid":30213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"點解連桃都唔食皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"798413b762a3e5caef197d06b0d1b95cc9b1d8a8","tid":595241,"uid":103799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"我食橙連皮食正好多"},{"pid":"c42f71f86617c8b2c578656be8782fc6d4f32d41","tid"